Shivani Photography — shivyank.com
===================================

A private photography portfolio app. React SPA frontend + FastAPI backend on AWS Lambda.
Authenticated via AWS Cognito. Images stored in S3, served via CloudFront CDN.

## Stack

- Frontend: React (Create React App), styled-components, Axios, amazon-cognito-identity-js
- Backend: FastAPI (Python 3.9), Mangum (Lambda adapter), Pillow, boto3
- Infrastructure: AWS Lambda, API Gateway, S3 (images + website hosting), CloudFront, Cognito

## Quick start

### Frontend
  cd frontend
  npm start          # dev server at localhost:3000

### Backend
  cd backend
  source venv/bin/activate
  uvicorn main:app --reload   # dev server at localhost:8000

### Deploy everything
  cd backend
  bash deploy_lambda.sh

This builds the Lambda zip (with Pillow Linux wheel), deploys to Lambda,
builds the React frontend, syncs to S3, and invalidates CloudFront.

## Key Features

- Cognito login (3 roles: Admin / Downloader / Viewer)
- 10-minute inactivity auto sign-out; 401 responses also trigger sign-out
- Upload via S3 presigned URLs (bypasses API Gateway 10 MB limit)
- Server-side thumbnail (400×267) + display (1200×800) image generation via Pillow
- EXIF auto-rotation on all resized images
- Latest-uploaded images first (offset-based pagination, sorted by LastModified)
- 60-second in-memory metadata cache (invalidated on upload/delete)
- All images served via CloudFront with 1-year Cache-Control headers
- Admin-only: upload, delete, stats, S3 connection status

